{"tid":557444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔巴士車禍】路祭現場多出一塊靈牌　事主仍在手術中","createTime":"2018-02-11T11:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T13:11:16.000Z","uid":89595,"like":334,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4487b35988641821ded40a2c3a975b27896ddd","tid":557444,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/190255_fa2824d8ae4ba2a19339a9e4fa102e03.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F190255_fa2824d8ae4ba2a19339a9e4fa102e03.jpeg&h=1b138268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔公路昨日傍晚發生嚴重車禍，至今有19人死亡、60多人受傷。今日下午約4時，有逾百人在車禍現場路祭，現場卻置有20個靈牌。本報致電政府新聞處查詢，對方引述根據醫管局提供最新資料回覆，目前車禍死者數目仍為19人。消息人士透露，第20個牌位屬於一名姓馮男子，事主現時仍在醫院接受手術。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518343684469\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518343684469&d=kiKBxHDjUeexk8ASMQHTr57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bb2bc880\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518343684469&h=a44047b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518343684469</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310c3fc7b709c970faea67e01d4ccdd66fe2dd69","tid":557444,"uid":89595,"like":797,"dislike":6,"score":791,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"邊個咁大整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5084b7a839d725cde6a679d6c227ea0d803b79a","tid":557444,"uid":105715,"like":567,"dislike":6,"score":561,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"開始幫埋閻王未審先判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/